title:StartNode
---
Jude: Hey! Y'all finally made it! I was startin' to get worried there.
Jude: As I've promised, I got some elixirs and other stuff that'll keep y'all alive.
Jude: It's nothing too crazy right now, but feel free to come back time to time to see if I cooked up something new!
Loveday: Thanks for this, really.
-> (Let's see what Jude's got.)
    <<open_shop Player>>
-> I think we're good for now.
===

title:NPCFight1Win
---
Jude: Hey. I got new stuff for ya! Wanna check it out?
Loveday: What is it?
Jude: It's GARLIC!!!!
<<unlock_garlic Player>>    
-> Sure gimme garlic.
    <<open_shop Player>>
-> I'm okay.
===

title:NPCFight1Lose
---
Jude: Hey. Y'all are Looking rough...
Jude: Here to buy somethin'?
-> Yes, we need to. 
    <<open_shop Player>>
-> Not right now. 
