title:ElsieF1W
---
Elsie: (Sulking.)
Loveday: She’s still sulking. 
	-> You know Dahlia’s just a realist.
        Elsie: Still…!
	Elsie: Without Dahlia…. or you and Vera here… what will happen to me?
