title: DahliaF1W
---
Dahlia: ...
Dahlia: What.
Loveday: Nothing.
Dahlia: Okay...?
Loveday: (Dahlia seems different.)

-> Was it what Elsie said?
    Loveday: Was it what Elsie said?
    Dahlia: Hm? Am I that obvious?
    Loveday: Yes. You sure did ruin the mood.
    Dahlia: Ugh, you’re one to talk, Mr. High-And-Mighty.
    Loveday: It’s not often I agree with her, but I too don’t appreciate you thinking we’d die so easily. 
    Dahlia: *Sigh*

-> Leave her be.
    Loveday: (Best not to pry. She'll snap out of it eventually.)

===

title:VeraStart
---
Vera: Uhh- Ah- Ehhhhhhh…
Vera: Dang, is there nothing left in this packet???
Vera: Not even a drop of blood left for me… 
Loveday: You can’t possibly be scrounging for scraps right before battle. 
Vera: Hey! I need to be energized before a fight, okay?!

===


title:VeraF1L
---
Vera: Are we gonna win this one???
Loveday: Dunno. We’ll see.
Vera: Aw man… I just wanna get a taste of victory…

===


title:VeraF1W
---
Vera: The stars are so bright today, I can’t take my eyes off them.
Loveday: (Are stars not visible where she’s originally from?)
	-> Do you like the stars?
	    Vera: Yes, I love the stars!
	    Vera: It’s only until recently I’ve learned the wonders that lie in the sky. 
        Loveday: I assume you’re not accustomed to seeing them this bright? You are from (insert main city here.) I heard the lights make it harder to see the stars.
        Vera: Wow, you’re correct!
        Vera: My days used to be filled with fog that was within arms-reach.

    -> Leave her to gaze.
===
